ame: fadeInUp;\"><div class=\"ss\"></div>\n<div class=\"ss1\"></div>\n<img src=\"../../images/weixintupian_20210224160842.jpg\">\n  \n  <div class=\"current wow fadeInUp animated\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">\n<div class=\"clearfix container\">\n    <div class=\"pull-left banner-tt\">\n\n\n\n流体力学研究所</div>\n    <div class=\"pull-left nav-b\">                <a href=\"../../index.htm\">首页</a>\n                &gt;\n                <a href=\"../../szqk.htm\">师资情况</a>\n                &gt;\n                <a href=\"../../szqk/szxx.htm\">师资信息</a>\n                &gt;\n                <a href=\"../../szqk/szxx/gclxx.htm\">工程力学系</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"clearfix container\"><ul class=\"pull-right banner-ul clearfix\">\n    \n    <li><a href=\"../../szqk/ys.htm\" title=\"院士\">院士</a></li>\n\n    \n    <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"../../szqk/szxx.htm\" title=\"师资信息\">师资信息</a></li>\n\n</ul></div>\n</div>\n  </div>\n\n<div class=\"container\">\n\n<div>\n\n\n<script language=\"javascript\" src=\"../../_dwr/interface/NewsvoteDWR.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"../../_dwr/engine.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/news/newscontent.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/ajax.js\"></script><form name=\"_newscontent_fromname\">\n\n<div style=\"background: #fff;\">\n\n       <div class=\"teach-top wow fadeInUp animated\" style=\"visibility: visible; animation-name: fadeInUp;\">\n            <div class=\"teach-top-img\"><img src=\"/__local/D/5F/E9/0FFF4E858C2725DA8DFA4ED9502_FF24607E_14F9C.jpg\"></div>\n            <div class=\"teacher-name\"><a>徐胜金</a></div>\n            <div class=\"teacher-p\">\n                <div class=\"row\">\n                    <div class=\"col-xs-6\">\n                                    <p>职称：副教授</p>\n                                    <p>电话：86+10+62788941</p>\n                                    <p>E-mail address：xu_shengjin@tsinghua.edu.cn</p>\n                    </div>\n                    \n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div> \n        <div id=\"vsb_content\"><div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">个人简介</div><div class=\"v_news_content\">\n<p class=\"vsbcontent_start\">徐胜金 博士 副教授</p>\n<p>地址：清华大学蒙民伟科技大楼N721</p>\n<p>E-mail:<a href=\"mailto:xu_shengjin@tsinghua.edu.cn\">xu_shengjin@tsinghua.edu.cn</a></p>\n<p>Phone: 86+10+62788941</p>\n</div><div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">教育背景</div><div class=\"jl-txt wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\"><h4><p>1999/09-2003/07 香港理工大学机械工程系, 博士.<br></p></h4>\n<p>1995/09-1997/07 哈尔滨工业大学航天工程与力学，硕士</p>\n<p>1988/09-1992/07 哈尔滨工业大学工程力学系 学士</p></div><div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">工作履历</div><div class=\"jl-txt wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\"><h4><p>2006/07- 今 清华大学航天航空学院, 副教授<br></p></h4>\n<p>2005/07-2006/06 SMME, RMIT University, 访问研究员</p>\n<p>2003/09-2005/06 香港理工大学机械工程系 博士后</p>\n<p>1992/07-1999/10 哈尔滨理工大学（哈尔滨电工学院） 讲师</p></div><div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">学术兼职</div><div class=\"jl-txt wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\"><h4><p>第7、8届实验流体力学专委会委员<br></p></h4>\n<p>中国汽车学会空气动力学分会委员</p></div><div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">研究领域</div><div class=\"jl-txt wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\"><h4><p>绕流、流致振动及控制、湍流实验研究、风洞实验<br></p></h4></div><div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">学术成果</div><div class=\"jl-txt wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\"><h4><p>[1] S.J. Xu, W.G. Zhang, L. Gan, M.G. Li and Y. Zhou, Experimental study of flow around polygon cylinders， Journal of Fluid Mechanics, 2017 812, 251-278.<br></p></h4>\n<p>[2] S.J. Xu, G. Lian and Y.Zhou, Flow interaction between a streamwise oscillating cylinder and a downstream stationary cylinder，Experiments in Fluids, 2016, 57(11): 173.</p>\n<p>[3] 胡站伟，焦立国，徐胜金，黄勇，基于多尺度重采样思想的类指数核函数构造，《电子与信息学报》, 2016, 38(7):1689-1695。</p>\n<p>[4] Qingyang Wang, Kun Song and Shengjin Xu, Experimental study of a spring-mounted wide-D-section cylinder in a cross flow, 2016, Fluid-structure-sound interactions and control, proceedings of the 3rd symposium on Fluid-structure-sound interactions and control. Springer-Verlag Berlin Heidelberg,pp395-399.</p>\n<p>[5] 王汉封, 徐胜金 2014 用POD方法研究有限长正方形棱柱尾流的双稳态现象, 空气动力学学报 [J]， 32, 827-833.</p>\n<p>[6] Qingyang Wang, Mogeng Li, Shengjin Xu, 2015 Experimental study on vortex induced vibration (VIV) of a wide-D-section cylinder in a cross flow, Theoretical &amp; Applied Mechanics Letters, 5, 20-24.</p>\n<p>[7] 杨可，黄浩，徐胜金，2014 组合小翼和翼梢喷流对翼尖涡的影响实验研究，实验流体力学 [J]，28，27-38。</p>\n<p>[8] Bai, HL， Zhou, Y， Zhang, WG，Xu, SJ， Wang, Y and Antonia, RA. 2014 Active control of a turbulent boundary layer based on local surface perturbation, Journal of Fluid Mechanics, 750, 316-354.</p>\n<p>[9] Wang, W. B., R. F. Hu, S. J. Xu and Z. N. Wu, 2013 Influence of Aspect Ratio on Tumbling Plates. Journal of Fluid Mechanics 733, 650-679.</p>\n<p>[10] Yang Ke and Xu ShengJin, 2011 Wing tip vortex structure behind an airfoil with flaps at the tip, Science China: Physics, Mechanics and Astronomy, 54(4), 743-747.</p>\n<p>[11] Xu SJ, Zhou Y and Ji YT. 2008 Two dimensionality of a cantilevered-cylinder wake in the presence of an oscillating upstream cylinder, Journal of Fluids and Structures, 24, 467-480.</p>\n<p>[12] Xu SJ, Zhou Y &amp; Wang MH. 2006 A symmetric binary vortex street behind a longitudinal oscillating cylinder. Journal of Fluid Mechanics, 556, 27-43.</p>\n<p>[13] Xu SJ, Zhou Y, Mi J 2004 Flow visualization behind a streamwise oscillating cylinder and a stationary cylinder in tandem arrangement. Journal of Visualization, 7 (3): 201-208.</p>\n<p>[14] Xu SJ, Zhou Y, So RMC 2003 Reynolds number effects on the flow structure behind two side-by-side cylinders. Physics of Fluids 15 (5): 1214-1219.</p>\n<p>[15] Xu SJ, Zhou Y and So RMC 2003 An analytical solution to the structural dynamics of an elastic cylinder in a cross flow. Dynamics of Continuous Discrete and Impulsive system-Series B-Applications &amp; Algorithms 10 (1-3): 345-362.</p>\n<p>[16] Zhou Y, Wang ZJ, So RMC, Xu SJ and Jin W 2001 Free vibrations of two side-by-side cylinders in a cross-flow. Journal of Fluids Mechanics 443: 197-229.</p>\n<p>[17] Xu SJ, Kong XR., Wang BL., Ma XR. and Zhang XC 2000 A method of equivalent analysis for static and dynamical behaviors of orthotropic honeycomb sandwich plates. ACTA Materiale Compositae Sinica, 17, 92-95. (in Chinese)</p>\n<p class=\"vsbcontent_end\">[18] Xu SJ, Song Y, Wang BL. and Ma XR 1998 Investigation of dynamical behaviors of orthotropic honeycomb sandwich plates. ACTA Materiale Compositae Sinica, 15, 74-80. (in Chinese)</p></div></div>\n\n     </div>\n</form>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"footer wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n      <div class=\"friends-box wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">\n        <div class=\"friends-left\">友情链接</div>\n    <a href=\"https://www.tsinghua.edu.cn/\" title=\"\" onclick=\"_addDynClicks(&quot;wburl&quot;, 1696534067, 71220)\">清华大学</a>\n\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"clearfix wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">\n        <div class=\"pull-left footer-logo\">                            <img src=\"../../images/logo.png\">\n</div>\n        <div class=\"pull-right footer-txt\"><!-- 版权内容请在本组件\"内容配置-版权\"处填写 -->\n<p>版权所有 © 清华大学京ICP备15006448号 京公网安备 110402430053 号&nbsp;</p><p>推荐ie8以上谷歌等浏览器浏览网页</p><p>联系方式：电话：010-62782434&nbsp; &nbsp;传真：010-62792407</p></div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n  </